[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "素材も集まったし、ここからはアタシの見せ場！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00332",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "今日は初めてのお客様もいるし、\nいつもより多めに回しちゃいますわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00333",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "錬金術は素人だけど、多めに回して大丈夫なの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00334",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そこは錬金術士の腕の見せどころっす！\nあと１時間ちょっとやるだけで",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00335",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "１時間はびっくりだわ。錬金術って、忍耐なのね……\nレスナも、それができてるってことよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00336",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ええと、これでも短いほうなんすけども……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00337",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "クレオは昔から一つ所に留まらないことには\n定評があったからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00338",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "それはリヒャルト兄さんも同じだと思うけど？\nっていうかいたんだ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00339",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "いたよ、ちょっと前から！\nメーヴェさんが合流したって知らせがあったから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00340",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "兄が、妹に舐められてる……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00341",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "とっても仲がいい兄妹ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00342",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "軽口が叩き合えるのも、家族の形の１つかもね。\nレスナは大人しかったわよ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00343",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そうだったんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00344",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "そうか、アルビーナは昔のレスナを知らないか。\nおのぼりさんだった頃の彼女から見違えたからなぁ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00345",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "私も今のレスナを知らないから、\n会うのが楽しみなのよね～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00346",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そういえば、お母さんとはもう何年も会ってないって\nレスナが言ってたような",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00347",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ええ。ウェルテックスとの戦いで行方不明になった\n愛しのユリウス……旦那を探して旅していたの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00348",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "彼を探して幾数年……十数年かな？\nもう結構長くなるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00349",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "多分大陸の南西地域にいるんじゃないかなって\nうろうろしてたんだけど、空振りばかりでね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00350",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "危険地帯の南西地域をうろうろって……\n南辺境を守ってた私からすると信じられないんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00351",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "そこはほら！　冒険者だし？\nで、放浪してたら聞こえてきたわけよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00352",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "頂獣を倒した錬金術士がいる。\nその名はレスナ・シュテルネンリヒト……って",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00353",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "それ、もう１年以上前の出来事なんだけどね。\n王国領ではない地域には情報が伝わるのが遅いから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00354",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "で、レスナはどうしてるんだろうと思って\n里帰りしたら実家にだーれもいない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00355",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ココシュカさん家で王都に行ったって聞いたから\n向かってみたら、ロマンさんと出会ったの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00356",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "こっちは九偉人のヘルトとゼロの対策を練っていてね。\nレスナたちは大変な目にあっているはずだろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00357",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "援軍はいくらあってもいい、そう思って事情を話して\nメーヴェさんにも神聖国まで来てもらったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00358",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "なるほど……１０年以上会ってないお母さんが\n助けに来たって知ったら、レスナ喜ぶだろうな～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00359",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "だといいけど……ねえ、今のあの子って、\nあなたたちから見てどういう錬金術士かしら？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00360",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "まずは……本が好きで難しい単語をよく知ってる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00361",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "なるほどね、確かに昔から本の虫だった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00362",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "そして強い意志を持った、とても優しい子ですよ。\n夢を追い、巨大な敵と戦っています",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00363",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "そう……強さは私譲り、優しさはユリウス譲りね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00364",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "直接の面識はないけれど、諸国の問題を解決し\nこの無数島群域でも知られる英雄って聞いてるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00365",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "とても、いい仲間に恵まれていると思うわ。\nその点は安心してもらって大丈夫",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00366",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "いやあほんと、親はなくとも子は育つというか、\n私を反面教師にしてるのかも？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00367",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……アタシにとっては、困ったときに\nそっと助けてくれる……とっても頼りになる、先輩です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00368",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "そっか、しっかり先輩やれてるのね。\nあの引っ込み思案だったレスナが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00369",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "私の知ってるレスナは幼くて、\n恋も、親への反抗もまだだった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00370",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "託せる人がいたとはいえ、夫を探すために\nほったらかしで家を飛び出して……酷い母親だけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00371",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "私とユリウスの自慢の子……レスナをありがとう。\nそしてこれからも、どうかよろしくお願いします",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00372",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]